{"type": "article", "id": 23201, "title": "文艺版咖啡包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121220LvmdgAno7KrHV9EP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组很文艺的咖啡包装设计，墨西哥平面设计公司 Behagen 认为人们很愿意了解咖啡背后的故事，因而在包装上用小号字写了大量关于咖啡的起源和背景，不禁让人联想起那些爱喝咖啡的作家以及与咖啡有关的书。盒子是黑色的，尽管区别口味时也用了彩色的纸，但色调仍然偏灰，非常干净素雅。<a href=\"http://www.behagen.mx/special-harvest\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121218Badrc6UeGXOf4wSD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121219XsU6HQGTtmZAk8fC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121219meVdCoUHPtY6NTaZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121219vUjgpEH7VskcZ6Bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121220L3q8zu97Ya1UDfXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}